flowchart TD
    input["用户输入 (字符串 or ContentBlockParam)"] --> mode_check{mode?}
    mode_check -->|"feature flag + Ultraplan 关键词"| ultraplan["Ultraplan 分支 → processSlashCommand"]
    mode_check -->|"mode === bash"| bash_branch["Bash 分支 → processBashCommand"]
    mode_check -->|"startsWith 斜杠"| slash_branch["斜杠命令分支 → processSlashCommand"]
    mode_check -->|其他| text_branch["普通文本分支 → processTextPrompt"]
    ultraplan --> attach_skip[附件提取: 跳过]
    bash_branch --> attach_bash[附件提取: 执行]
    slash_branch --> attach_slash[附件提取: 执行]
    text_branch --> attach_text[附件提取: 执行]
